               <h5 class="text-uppercase  font-weight-bold">Privacy Policy :</h5>
               <p class="text-justify small text-dark">This Privacy Policy is intended to inform you regarding the personal information that may be collected through ellocart.com and how we use, share, and protect that information.</p>
