               <p class="text-justify small text-dark">We will gather individual data by legal and reasonable means and, where fitting, with the information or assent of the individual concerned.</p>
               <p class="text-justify small text-dark">Personal information ought to be important to the reasons for which it is to be utilized, and, to the degree essential for those reasons, ought to be exact, finished, and updated.</p>
               <p class="text-justify small text-dark">We will protect individual data by using security shields against misfortune or burglary, and also unapproved access, divulgence, duplicating, use, or alteration.</p>
